  "2351700": {
    "name": "The Gun is Good",
    "steam_appid": 2351700,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款动作类 Roguelike 俯视射击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >子弹天堂对抗弹幕地狱，人与恶魔群潮殊死对抗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集无数强力枪械，屠戮千军万魔，并利用符文之力不断壮大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被困于无垠延伸的星界，数不尽的嗜血恶魔步步紧逼——形势岌岌可危。但至少，你还有枪！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越奇异维度，在层出不穷的环境中与愈加强大、愈发凶狠的敌人战斗，努力寻找回家的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/425d09c1f8d9353cfd32d015ff724f00.webp?t=1762425753\" width=618 height=2 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恶魔无穷无尽，但枪足够强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用你那一整套强力（甚至极其强力）的枪械，摧毁挡在你面前的一切，无论是恶魔还是坚固墙体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恶魔掌握着符文——星界的通用货币。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/feffe1e7dc7156aef0abcb50abd6f412.poster.avif?t=1762425753\" width=618 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/feffe1e7dc7156aef0abcb50abd6f412.webm?t=1762425753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/425d09c1f8d9353cfd32d015ff724f00.webp?t=1762425753\" width=618 height=2 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越每次游玩都变化莫测的奇异维度地图，布局与特性各不相同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以选择风险较低但奖励较少的路径，或挑战自身极限以获取更丰厚的回报。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索危险与安全区域，最终抵达并挑战强大的恶魔领主。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/ca2a6d56ae21c4b429ae4af3bdfed60e.poster.avif?t=1762425753\" width=646 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/ca2a6d56ae21c4b429ae4af3bdfed60e.webm?t=1762425753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/425d09c1f8d9353cfd32d015ff724f00.webp?t=1762425753\" width=618 height=2 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掠夺或购买数十种各具特性、优劣分明的枪械。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过数十种改装组件进一步强化它们的威力与功能，组合方式多如星辰，变化无穷。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/90dc73a6cb9b5cb22e8a024dafd7f3ec.poster.avif?t=1762425753\" width=800 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/90dc73a6cb9b5cb22e8a024dafd7f3ec.webm?t=1762425753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/90dc73a6cb9b5cb22e8a024dafd7f3ec.mp4?t=1762425753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现各类道具，助你在旅途中更进一步。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/3f9c57d7f9a8eb8b42c3d7edfe3094ff.poster.avif?t=1762425753\" width=604 height=502 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/3f9c57d7f9a8eb8b42c3d7edfe3094ff.webm?t=1762425753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/3f9c57d7f9a8eb8b42c3d7edfe3094ff.mp4?t=1762425753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/425d09c1f8d9353cfd32d015ff724f00.webp?t=1762425753\" width=618 height=2 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >符文有多种用途，可用来激活数十种不同的符文能力强化角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还能用于购买道具、枪械与弹药。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找方式为枪械附加改装组件，进一步提升其威力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/ae913f804438afa9be46a0ae3bfae5c5.poster.avif?t=1762425753\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/ae913f804438afa9be46a0ae3bfae5c5.webm?t=1762425753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351700/extras/ae913f804438afa9be46a0ae3bfae5c5.mp4?t=1762425753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
